If you are wanting help please type <help> and see available commands.
Finding you can't see anything? Try the spell Infravision.
As a newbie please use help <command> before you ask!
The Donation room is really good for finding equipment!
The Riverside Tavern is a good place to rejuvinate!
The area command is fantastic for finding zones to play in!
We have a remort system type help <remort> to learn about it!
